00:02:38.222 --> 00:02:40.862
aí eu quebrei a seta do volante

00:02:40.862 --> 00:02:43.922
e enfiei na minha perna

00:02:43.922 --> 00:02:46.482
pra concentrar a dor, cara

00:02:46.482 --> 00:02:48.882
